---
// Tarjeta básica - Una tarjeta simple con sombra
---

<div class="card-showcase">
  <h3>Tarjeta Básica</h3>
  <div class="card-basic">
    <div class="card-header">
      <h4>Título de la Tarjeta</h4>
    </div>
    <div class="card-body">
      <p>Esta es una tarjeta básica con contenido simple. Incluye un título y descripción con un diseño limpio y moderno.</p>
      <button class="card-btn">Leer más</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .card-showcase {
    padding: 2rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-light);
    border-radius: 8px;
    background: var(--card-bg-light);
    margin: 1rem 0;
    transition: background 0.3s ease, border-color 0.3s ease;
  }

  html.dark .card-showcase {
    background: var(--card-bg-dark);
    border-color: var(--border-dark);
  }

  .card-showcase h3 {
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
    color: #333;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  html.dark .card-showcase h3 {
    color: var(--header-text-dark);
  }

  .card-basic {
    background: var(--card-bg-light);
    border-radius: 12px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease, background 0.3s ease;
    max-width: 300px;
  }

  html.dark .card-basic {
    background: var(--card-bg-dark);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
  }

  .card-basic:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
  }

  html.dark .card-basic:hover {
    box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
  }

  .card-header {
    padding: 1.5rem 1.5rem 0;
  }

  .card-header h4 {
    margin: 0;
    color: #333;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  html.dark .card-header h4 {
    color: var(--header-text-dark);
  }

  .card-body {
    padding: 1rem 1.5rem 1.5rem;
  }

  .card-body p {
    color: #666;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem 0;
  }

  html.dark .card-body p {
    color: #a0aec0;
  }

  .card-btn {
    background: #667eea;
    color: white;
    border: none;
    padding: 8px 16px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background 0.3s ease;
  }

  .card-btn:hover {
    background: #5a67d8;
  }
</style>
